- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper discusses the development of autonomously driving vehicles for urban environments, which falls under the field of robotics. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also likely as the paper discusses the need for further investigation in software engineering to achieve the goal of driving safely and reliably through urban environments. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper discusses the development of anticipatory vehicles, which involves the use of AI techniques. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also possible as the paper discusses the development of a cyber-physical system for autonomous driving. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is less likely but still possible as the paper may discuss the use of machine learning techniques in the development of autonomous driving systems.
